#: app/templates/www/features.html:4
msgid ""
"Orders with 8-step workflow, drawings and CAD, customer material on "
"stock, product catalog, multi-tenant isolation. Built specifically for "
"manufacturing SMEs."
msgstr ""
"Aufträge mit 8-Schritte-Workflow, Zeichnungen und CAD, Kundenmaterial im "
"Lager, Produktkatalog, Multi-Tenant-Isolation. Speziell für produzierende"
" KMU entwickelt."

#: app/templates/www/features.html:13
