msgstr "Was Assoluto alles kann"

#: app/templates/www/features.html:16
msgid ""
"Not a generic CRM. Built for manufacturing — drawings, revisions, "
"deadlines, customer material on stock."
msgstr ""
"Kein generisches CRM. Für die Produktion gebaut — Zeichnungen, "
"Revisionen, Termine, Kundenmaterial im Lager."

