#: app/templates/www/features.html:87
msgid ""
"PDF, PNG, JPG, DWG, DXF, STEP, STL — anything the shop floor needs. "
"Direct upload to S3 (up to 50 MB / file). Thumbnails for PDFs and images."
msgstr ""
