#: app/templates/www/self_hosted.html:119
msgid ""
"Assoluto is released under AGPL-3.0. Practically: you may run it free of "
"charge, modify it, and host it — even commercially. If you offer a "
"modified version as a service to third parties, you must publish your "
"modifications under the same licence. For a closed-source deployment, "
"contact us for a commercial licence."
msgstr ""
"Assoluto wird unter AGPL-3.0 veröffentlicht. Praktisch: Sie dürfen es "
